-- RBC Capital Hires 4Cast's Turner as Australia, N.Z. Currencies Strategist
-- Candice Zachariahs
-- 2010-07-16T00:52:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/rbc-capital-hires-4cast-s-turner-as-australia-n-z-currencies-strategist.html

          
          
             RBC Capital Markets, a unit of
Canadaâ€™s largest lender, hired  Michael Turner  as a fixed-income
and currency strategist covering Australia and New Zealand for
its global research team.  
 Sydney-based Turner, who previously worked as an economist
with 4Cast Ltd., joined RBC Capital Markets on July 6 and will
report to senior strategists  Su-Lin Ong  in Sydney and  Sue Trinh 
in Hong Kong, said  Elize Van Graan , human resources manager at
the bank. Turner, 28, will assist in generating trade ideas and
in forecasting economic data, interest rates, bonds and currency
levels, she said.  
